        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks LJ for his book [<hi rend="italic">Observations in meteorology</hi> (1858)].</p>  
<p>CD has been working on his species book [<hi rend="italic">Natural selection</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Has become dreadfully heterodox on immutability of species.</p>
            <p>His work on pigeons: variation under domestication throws the greatest light on variation in a state of nature.</p>
        </abstract>
